data.description: Assumable VA at 3.625%!! The perfect blend of luxury living and country charm! This exquisite 4bd/2ba custom home, nestled on 6 acres on the sought after Newaukum Hill! If you've ever dreamed of owning a farm complete with gardens and fruit trees, this is your opportunity! Imagine waking up to the tranquil sounds of nature, sipping your morning coffee on the spacious deck, and enjoying the serenity of your very own woodland oasis. Fenced pastures with a large stall, tackroom, dog kennels, and a chicken coop! Inside, the home boasts spacious living areas, an open area kitchen, and finished basement. Don't miss the chance to experience the lifestyle you've always envisioned. Come take a tour and make your dream of country living a reality.
